bench = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "mini-app-fuzzer"

doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"

autoexamples = true

[dependencies]

[features]
default = ["std"]

[profile.release]
opt-level = 3
debug = true
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
